@startuml mvp-lifecycle-states
title AKDB Agent-Authoring - MVP Lifecycle States
[*] --> planned
planned : seq assigned (monotonic); attached to topic(s)
planned --> in_progress : work starts
in_progress --> shipped : increment delivered (shipped_at set)
shipped : appears in generated changelog at its seq
shipped --> superseded : a later MVP supersedes (mvp_supersedes)
planned --> superseded : dropped before work
in_progress --> superseded : abandoned
superseded --> [*]
note right of shipped
  Temporal order = seq / shipped_at
  Contextual order = mvp_touches_topic + mvp_* edges
end note
@enduml
